text: De somniorum diuersiitate secundum ordinem abcharii Danielis prophetebe swefena mistlicnesse æfter endebyrdnessæ abecedes danielis þæs witegan.
Aues in somnis qui uiderit & cum ipsis pugnauerit, lites aliquas significatfugelas on swefenum seþe gesyhð & mid him winneð saca sume hit getacnað.
Aues in somnis capere, lucrum significatfugelas on swefnum gefon gestreon hit getacnað.
Aues aliquid a se rapuisse, damnum significatfugelas sumþincg fram him gegripan <hearm> hit getacnað.
Asinos uel edos uiderit, crimen negotii significatassan oððe hecenu gesihð gylt ceapes hit getacnað.
Arma in somnis portare, tutamentum significatwæpnu on swæfnum beran bewerunge hit getacnað.
Asinos edere, laborem significatassan etan geswinc hit getacnað.
Asinos clamantes aut solutos currere, aliquam litem aduersari<../images/etail.gif>significatassan clipiende oððe <untiede> yrnan sume sace wyðerwyrdnysse hit getacnað.
Aues bullientes uiderit, inimicorum malam locutionem significatfugeles sceottende gesihð feonda yfele sprece hit getacnað.
Arbores cum fructu uiderit, lucrum exsperatum significattreow mid wæstme gesihð gestreon gewilnode hit getacnað.
Arbores ascendere, aliquam dignitatem optinebittreow uppastigan sumne wyrðscype he begyt.
<Aerem> limpidem uiderit, negotii expeditionem significatweder hlutter gesihð ceapes ferðrunge hit getacnað.
A bestiis qui si uiderit infestare, ab inimicis superabiturfram wyldeorum seþe hine gesihð ehtan fram feondum he byð oferswiðed.
<Arcum> tendere uel sagittas mittere, laborem uel anxietatem significatbogan bendan oððe flan asendan geswinc oððe angsumnysse getacnaþ.
Anullum in somnis uiderit, locum exsperatum significatring on swefnum gesihð stowe gewilnode hit getacnaþ.
<Anullum> in somnis accipere, securitatem significatring on swefnum underfon carleaste getacnaþ.
Anullum dare, dampnum significatring syllan hearm getacnaþ.
Aurum in somnis trectare, expeditionem negotii significatgold on swefnum handlian forðunge ceapes getacnað.
Absinthium bibere, litem grauem significatwermod drincan sace hefige hit getacnaþtacnaþ.
Acetum bibere in somnis, infirmitatem significateced drincan on swefnum untrumnysse getacnaþ.
<Agrimoniam> edere, nuntium fedum significatgarclifan etan ærende fullic getacnaþ.
Alba aut splendida se uestire, iocunditatem significathwite oððe beorhte hine gescrydan wynsumnysse getacnaþ.
Alba aut splendida se uestire, iocunditatem significathwite oððe beorhte hine gescrydan wynsumnysse getacnaþ.
Arare qui se uiderit, labores maximas ei obueniunterian seþe hine gesihð swincu mæste him ongean cumað.
Barba sibi tondi, dampnum significatbeard him beon bescoren <hearm> hit getacnaþ.
Bracas in somnis uiderit, securitatem significatbraccas on swefnum gesihð <carleaste> getacnaþ.
Bordore sedere deceptionem negotii significaton folan sittan swicunge ceapes hit getacnaþ.
Brutum se uiderit, infirmitatem significatwilde hine gesihð untrumnysse getacnaþ.
<Brachia> ualida habere, incrementum significateormas strange habban wexinge hit getacnaþ.
Bestias domare qui se uiderit, gratiam aduersariorum significatwilde deor temian seþe hine gesihð gyfe oððe þanc wiðerwinnena getacnaþ.
Bestias currentes uiderit, aliquam turbationem significatwilde deor yrnende gesihð sume gedræfednysse getacnaþ.
Balneo se lauare, anxietatem significaton beþe hine þwean anxsumnesse getacnaþ.
Barbatum se uiderit, ornamentum significatgebyrdne hine gesihð glæncge getacnað.
Byrrum album habere, letitiam significatoferslop hwit haban blisse getacnaþ.
Byrrum coloreum habere, nuntium fedum significatoferslop bleofah habban ærende fullic getacnaþ.
<Bella> uel barbaros uiderit, letitiam in publico patetgefeohtu oððe heþene gesihð blisse on openum hit openað.
Butirum edere, nuntium bonum significatbuteran etan hærende god getacnaþ.
Boues pascentes uiderit agoniam negotii significatoxan grasiende gesihð sige ceapas getacnaþ.
Boues dormientes uiderit, malitiam negotii significatoxan slapende gesihð yfelnysse ceapes getacnaþ.
Bestias loquentes uiderit, molestias graues significatwilde deor sprecende gesihð teonan hefige getacnaþ.
Clamide uestiri securitatem significatmid rocce beon gescrid orsorhnysse getacnaþ.
Coronam cuiusque rei accipere letitiam significatcynehelm gewilces þinges onfon blisse hit getacnað.
Cecum qui se uiderit, inpeditionem significatblindne seþe hine gesihð lettincge getacnaþ.
C<../images/etail.gif>lum flamineum uiderit, aliquas iniquitates in toto orbe obueniuntheofen ligenne gesihð sume unrihtwisnysse on eallum embhwyrfte ongean cumað.
<Cucumeres> aut cucurbitas uiderit in somnis, infirmitatem significathwerhwettan oððe cyrfet gesihð on swefnum untrumnysse getacnaþ.
<Ceram> aridam edere, lites cum importunis significatwex drige etan saca mid ungecoplicum getacnaþ.
Columbas uiderit aliquam tristitiam significatculfran gesihð sume unrotnysse getacnaþ.
Carcere qui se uiderit, aliquam sollicitudinem uel calumpniam significaton cwearterne seþe hine gesihð sume carfulnesse oððe teonan getacnaþ.
Caput album habere, lucrum significat<heafod> wit habban gestreon getacnaþ.
Caput sibi tondi, dampnum significatheafod him beon gescoren hearm getacnaþ.
Calciamento nouo calciari, lucrum ex insperato significatmid gescy niwum beon gescod gestreon of ungewenedum getacnaþ.
Calciamento ueteri calciari, deceptionem significatmid gescy ealdum beon gescod swicunge getacnaþ.
Clauos colligere uel facere, laborem significatspicyngas gadirian oððe wyrcean geswinc hit getacnað.
Canes latrantes uiderit, uel eis infestare, inimici tui te superare querunt significathundas beorcynde gesihð oððe him laðhetan fynd þine þe oferswiðan secað.
Canes ludere uiderit, gratiam significathundas <plegan> gesihð þanc hit getacnað.
Caput lauare, ab omni metu & omni periculo liberabitur<heafod> þwean fram ælcum ege & ælcere fræcennysse he bið alesed.
Caseum recentem accipere, lucrum significatcyse geongne onfon gestreon getacnaþ.
Salsum si fuerit, litem significatsealt gif he bið sace hit getacnað.
Camelos uidere & ab eis se uiderit infestare, litem significatolfendas geseon & fram him gesihð laðhetan, sace hit getacnaþ.
Carbones qui se uiderit edere, inimici tui de te mala loquunturgleda seþe hine gesihð etan fynd þine be þe yfela sprecað.
Cancellos uiderit aut in eis se reclusum uideat, in aliqua calumpnia uel custodia detinetureahþyrlu gesihð oððe on him hine belocene geseo on sumum teonan oððe on hæftnoðe bið gehæfd.
<Cartam> scribere aut legere nuntium fedum significatcartan <writan> oððe rædan ærende fullic hit <getacnað>.
Cibum uomere dampnum significatmete spiwan hearm hit getacnað.
Ceroma uomere lites significatspiwan saca hit getacnaþ.
<Currere> qui se uiderit & non potest, inpeditionem significatyrnan seþe hine gesihþ & he ne mæg lettinge hit getacnað.
Curru sedere, litem grauem significaton cræte sittan sace hefyge hit getacnað.
Ceram uel cereos uiderit gaudium significatwex oððe taperas gesihð blisse hit getacnat.
Cum mortico fabulare lucrum significatmid deadum spellian gestrion hit getacnaþ.
Cum sorore concumbere dampnum significatmid his swuster gelicgan hearm hit getacnaþ.
Cum matre securitatem significatmid his meder orsorhnysse hit getacnaþ.
Cum uirgine concumbere anxietatem significatmid medene gelicgan <angsumnesse> hit.
Cum coniuge sua concumbere anxietatem significatmid his gemacan gelicge angsumnysse hit.
Codicellos cuiusque rei accipere uel legere aut legente audire, felicitatem temporis significatbec gewilces þinges onfon oððe rædan oððe rædende lestan geselþe timam hit getacnað.
Cum plures se uiderit aliquam calumniam grauem significatþonne man hine gesihð sumne teonan hefine hit.
Custodias qui uiderit deceptionem significatheordredena seþe gesihð swicunge hit getacnað.
Cimbala aut salteria aut corda tangere lites significatcimbalan oððe psalteras oððe strengas ætrinan saca hit.
Citharam uiderit securitatem negotii significathearpan gesihð orsorhnesse ceapes hit getacnaþ.
Cum mortuo loqui grande lucrum significatmid deadum sprecan micel gestrion hit.
Coruscationes uiderit lucrum significatligræsceas gesihð orsorhnesse hit getacnaþ.
Dentes suos cadere aliquis de parentibus suis morieturteð his feallan sum of his magum swylt.
Dentes inferiores aut maxillares cui ceciderint si cum sanguine aut sine dolore, alienus erit a parentibusteð neoðeran oððe tuxas þana afeallað gif mid blode oððe butan sare fræmde he bið fram magum.
Domo sua sacrificare incrementum letitie significaton huse his offrian wexincge oððe blisse hit getacnaþ.
Domum suam cecidisse dampnum cum pluribus significathus his feallan hearm mid manegum hit getacnaðDomum cecidisse & destruere dampnum significathus feallan & towyrpan hearm hit getacnaþ.
Domum suam ardere uiderit periculum uite significathus his byrnan gesyhð fræcenysse lifes getacnaþ.
Dulcia edere in multis criminibus opprimitur significatswete etan on manegum leahtrum bið ofsett hit getacnaþ.
Dalmatica uestire sibi lucrum significat ex seminemid biscoprocce scrydan him gestreon getacnað of cynne.
Dracones uiderit aliquam dignitatem significatdracan gesihð sumne wyrðscipe hit getacnaþ.
Equo albo sedere euentum bonum significoon horse hwitum sittan belimp got getacnaþ.
Equo nigro sedere anxietatem significoon horse sweartan sittan anxsumnesse getacnaþEquo flauo sedere, detrimentum significoon horse gelewum sittan hynðe getacnaþ.
Equo baio sedere, expeditionem significoon horse dunnan sittan ferðrunge getacnaþ.
Equo castaneo sedere, negotium fedum significoon horse brunum sittan ceap fulne getacnaþ.
Equos solutos currere aut ab eis infestare, dampnum significathors wilde yrnan oððe fram him hearmian hearm getacnaþ.
Ebriosum se uiderit, infirmitatem significodruncenne hine gesihð untrumnesse hit getacnaþ.
Eunuchos uiderit, dampnum significobelysnode gesihð hearm getacnaþ.
Elephantum uiderit infestum, aliquam accusationem significatylp gesihð laðne oððe gramne sume wrohte hit getacnað.
Eborum trectare, inpeditionem significoylpesban handlian lettincge getacnaþ.
Eborum emere aut uendere, tristitias maximas significatylpesban becgan oððe beceapan unrotnyssa mæste getacnaþ.
Farinam in somnis trectare, incrementum negotii significatmelu on swefnum handlian eacan ceapas getacnaþ.
Ferro percussum uiderit, sollicitudinem significatmid isene geslægene gesihð carfulnysse getacnaþ.
Ferrum cuiusque rei trectare, aliquas infirmitates significatisen gewylces þinges handlian sume untrumnyssa hit getacnaþ.
Faciem suam in quacunque re uiderit uita longa ei daturansine his on swawilcum þinge gesihð lif lang him bid geseald.
Faciem formosam se habere, auxilium & honorem ampliorem significatansine hiwlice hine habban fultum & wyrðmynt rumran getacnaþ.
Faciem turpem habere, multis criminibus subprimituransine fullice habban mid manegum bið ofþryccend.
Flumen turbulentum uiderit, offensiones significatflod drof gesihð æbyliigða hit getacnaþ.
Frumenta aliqua trectare, infirmitatem significathwætas sume andlian untrumnysse getacnaþ.
Fratrem uel sororem uiderit, a pessimis ulceribus fatigaturbroðer oððe swuster gesihð fram wyrstum wundum bið geswenct.
Fossam uiderit & in ea ceciderit, aliquam calumpniam significatpitt gesihð & on þane befealð sume teonan hit getacnaþ.
Fontem in domo sua uiderit aperiri, incrementum uel letitiam significatwylspring on huse his gesihð beon geopenad eacan oððe blisse getacnaþ.
Formicas quascumque uiderit lites maximas significatæmyttan swawilce gesihð saca þa mæstan getacnaþ.
Flumen in domo sua introire, periculum ipse patieturflod on huse his infaran fræcendnysse he þolað.
Fantasmas uiderit, lucrum ex insperato significatscinlacu gesihð gestreon of ungewendum hit getacnaþ.
Ficum uiderit, lites cum inportunis significatfictreow gesihð saca mid ungedafenlicum getacnaþ.
Ficum nigrum accipere, tristitiam significatfictreow sweart onfon unrotnyssa getacnaþ.
Folium cum uiuo accipere & bibere, infirmitatem significatlof mid wine onfon & <drincan> untrumnysse getacnaþ.
Folia cum recente uino accipere & bibere, felicitatem temporis significatleaf mid niwan wine niman & <drincan> geselðe timan getacnaþ.
Filosophos uiderit disungi, dampnum significatuðwitan gesihð twysehtan henðe getacnaþ.
Filios aut filias nasci uiderit, incrementum significatsuna oððe dohtra beon acennede gesihð eacum getacnað.
Gladiatorem se factum uiderit, dampnum fedum significatswurdboran hine gewordene gesihð hearm fullic getacnaþ.
Gladium ferre & de ipso ludere, anxietatem significatswurd beran & be him plegean unheaðnysse getacnaþ.
G.adiantes expectare, uicinas litas maximas significatswurdwegede anbidian gehende saca mæste getacnaþ.
Gemmam de anulo perdidisse, aliquid admittitgimm of ringe forleosan sumþinc forlæt.
Gallinam oua parere, lucrum cum sollicitudine significathenne ægru lecgan gestreon mid carfulnysse getacnaþ.
Gallinam cum pulcinis uiderit, <negotii> incrementum significathenne mid cicenum gesihð ceapas eacan getacnaþ.
Gentiles pugnantes uiderit & ab eis infestare, lites cum periculo significathæþene feohtende gesihð & fram him cidan saca mid fræcednysse ge.

Grandinem in somnis, tristitiam significathagol on swefnum unrotnysse getacnaþ.
Grandinem in somnis uiderit, dampnum crudele significathagol on swefnum gesihð hearm welreowne getacnaþ.

Hospites habere, inuidiam significatcuman habban andan getacnaþ.
Herculem uiderit amicitiam iungitgesihð freodscipe fegð.
Hominem occidere tutamentum significatmann ofslean bewerunge getacnaþ.
Imperatorem se factum aliquem honorem significatcasere hine beon gewordene wyrðscype getacnaþ.
In platea uel palatio deambulare anxietatem significaton strete oððe on palentan abutangan uneaðnysse getacnaþ.
Incendia in quocumque loco uiderit, aliquod periculum significatbrynas on gewilcre stowe gesihð sume fræcednysse getacnaþ.
In flumen notare anxietatem significaton flod swymman anxsumnesse getacnaþ.
In fonte se lauare, lucrum significaton wille hine þwean <gestreon> getacnaþ.
In mare se lauare letitiam significaton se hine þwean blisse getacnað.
In gurgite sordido lauare aliquam accusationem significaton wæle fulum þwean sume wrohte getacnaþ.
In mare cecidisse lucrum significaton sæ feallan gestreon getacnaþ.
In piscina cecidisse gaudium significaton mere feallan blisse.
In gurgite sordido cecidisse aliquam calumpniam significaton wæle fulan feallan sumne teonan getacnaþ.

Infirmitates aliquas uiderit, sollicitudinem significaton trumnyssa sume gesihð carfulnysse getacnaþ.
In theatrum uel in amphitheatrum exspectare se uiderit tumultum aliquem significaton <plegstowe> oððe on wafungstowe andbidian hine gesihð styrunge sume getacnaþ.
In pomerio ambulare, anxietatem grauem significaton æppeltune gan anxsumnysse hefige getacnaþ.
In tabula se pingi uiderit uita longa ei daturon brede hine beon gemetne lif lang him bið geseald.
Luna cingi, tutamento significatbeon gegyrd trymniige.
Luna perdere fidei salutationem significatforleosan geleafan tolysinge getacna.
Luna aurea cingere inuidiam significatgyldenne bygyrdan andan getacnaþ.
Luna pertica cingi, ualitudines significatstragnysse getacnaþ.
Lunam claram uiderit inuidiam significatmonan beorhtne gesihð blisse getacnaþ.
Lunas duas uiderit, inuidiam significatmonan twegen gesihð andan getacnaþ.
Lunam sanguinem uiderit damnum significatmonan blodigne gesihð hearm getacnaþ.
Lunam de celo cecidisse uel ascendere uiderit laborem significatmonan of heofene feallan oððe upastigan gesihð geswinc getacnaþ.
Lunam albam uiderit lucrum significatmonan wittne gesihð gestreon getacnaþ.
Lunam colores habere damnum significatmonan bleoh habban hynðe getacnaþ.
Lardum trectare aliquis de parentibus eius morieturspic handlian sum of his magum swylt.
Linea uestimenta lauare uidere dampnum significatlinene claðas waxan gesihð hearm getacnaþ.
Lineam uestem uestire aliquam egritudinem significatlinen reaf scredan sume seocnysse getacnaþ.
Leonem currentem uiderit, expeditionem negotii significatleon yrnende gesihð ferðrunge ceapas getacnaþ.
Leonem dormientem uiderit malignum negotium significatleon slæpende gesihð <awyrigedne> cep getacnaþ.
Leonem infestare inimici seditionem significatleon wedan feondes gestric getacnaþ.
Legatum se uiderit inpeditionem significatærendraca gesihð lettige getacnaþ.

Luminaria se uiderit securitatem significatleohtfatu hine gesihð orsorhnysse getacnaþ.
Lapides mittere egritudinem significatstanes asendan seocnesse getacnaþ.
Litigare in somnis negotii incrementum significatcidan on swefnum ceapes eacan getacnaþ.

Maris pisces uiderit anxietatem grauem significatsæfixas gesihð anxsumnysse hefige getacnaþ.
Manus sibi inquinatas uiderit opera iniqua significathanda him befylde gesihð weorca unrihte getacnaþ.

<Migrare> deceptionem significatfaran bigswicæ getacnaþ.
